Quickstrike:




Quickstrike watched as Stingtra bolted out of his sight. "What ah do?" he 
said to himself. Maybe she didn't like him. Maybe she did, and didn't want 
to show it. Quickstrike was dumbfounded about it. He went on about himself 
and captured a last fish. He went back to the shore and ate both of them. 
Afterwards he transformed to his robot mode and jogged back to the Predacon 
cave. He knew she would be there. He thought of asking what went wrong. He 
ought to, maybe it was something unconscious he did, and he would remind 
himself never to do it again.

He had forgotten about his fatigueness, and at the entrance of the cave, his 
legs went out on him. His feet spat sparks after he fell.
